metadata.name: Doodle Mutant Ape #1
metadata.description: Back in the day, When the world was devastated by a nuclear disaster, the Doodle Mutant Apes emerged out of the scenario. The imbalance has caused a series of natural and virological disasters. Of all the primates in the world, only the Apes resisted the cataclysm, but radiation played as the catalyst for their evolution and developed various mutations.
